# Netflix SQL Analysis

## Project Overview
This project analyzes a Netflix-style dataset using MySQL Workbench. The goal is to explore the data and answer business questions using SQL.

## Dataset
- Dataset: Netflix Titles
- Total Records: 1000
- Database: MySQL

## SQL Concepts Used
- SELECT
- WHERE
- ORDER BY
- GROUP BY
- HAVING
- Aggregate Functions
- CASE WHEN
- JOINS
- Subqueries
- CTE
- Window Functions
- Views
- Indexes

## Tools Used
- MySQL Workbench
- SQL
- GitHub

